GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/mailbox/unread?pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Starred (paged)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/mailbox/starred?pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Spam (paged)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/mailbox/spam?pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Trash (paged)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/mailbox/trash?pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Accept: application/json

###

# ----------------------------
# Labels
# ----------------------------

### Get Labels
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/labels
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Label
# @name createLabel
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/labels
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
 "name": "Work",
 "color": "#FF5733"
}

###

### Assign Label
# Replace labelId and mailId with IDs from responses
@LabelGuid =00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@MailRecipientGuid =00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/labels/{{LabelGuid}}/assign/{{MailRecipientGuid}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}

###

### Unassign Label
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v{{API_Version}}/labels/{{LabelGuid}}/unassign/{{MailRecipientGuid}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT}}

###
